One of the oldest and biggest masjid in Satara city.

Situated on main road, surrounded by greenery. Clean and hygienic. Washrooms are very clean and hygienic with a clean wazu place.

Parking is available for both two and four wheelers. It's odd and even parking system.

Zohar is at 1:30pm
Juma is at 2:10 pm

It is centre of Satara City well connected with local buses , Out station buses and autos to reach any corner of city. ST stand is nearly 8 to 10 minutes distance by walking and Railway station is approximately 6.8 km distance. The followers of this masjid is local shopkeepers and Travellers mostly. Namaz is offered 5 time with Friday's and Eid. This place is good for travellers for offering Namaz.
